## Active Themes

Current themes in design system:

### 1. Cosmos (default)
- Space theme with 150 moving stars
- Stars have autonomous movement with boundary collision
- Comets animation
- Deep purple color palette

### 2. Sunset
- Warm gradient background
- Fireflies with floating animation
- Orange/pink color scheme

### 3. VS Code Dark
- Code symbols animation (35 floating symbols)
- VS Code color palette
- Primary: #007acc, Background: #1e1e1e

All themes use consistent color structure:
```typescript
theme.colors = {
  primary: {
    main, light, dark,
    bg, bgHover, bgActive,
    border, borderHover, borderGlow,
    text, glow
  },
  neutral: { bg, bgDark, border },
  text: { primary, secondary, muted },
  gradient: { title, card }
}
```

